description: [``botocore``] Adds FileConfiguration to Amazon AppIntegrations CreateDataIntegration supporting scheduled downloading of third party files into Amazon Connect from sources such as Microsoft SharePoint.
[``botocore``] This release updates the documentation regarding Get/Update DataCellsFilter
[``botocore``] Added support for cross-account Multi-Region Access Points. Added support for S3 Replication for S3 on Outposts.
[``botocore``] This release adds tagging support to the following Network Instance APIs : Instantiate, Update, Terminate.
[``botocore``] This release extends Wisdom CreateKnowledgeBase API to support SharePoint connector type by removing the @required trait for objectField
